### Variables

@baseUrl = localhost:3000/dev

@contentType = application/json



# basic request
http://{{baseUrl}}


### Get all Tasks
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails


### Get one Task
GET http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails/{{emailId}}


### Create a new task
# @name createEmail
POST http://{{baseUrl}}/api/emails
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

